message.text:
𝑴𝑬𝑴𝑩𝑬𝑹𝑺𝑯𝑰𝑷 𝑨𝑷𝑷𝑳𝑰𝑪𝑨𝑻𝑰𝑶𝑵 | 𝑯𝑼𝑳𝑰𝑵𝑮 𝑨𝑹𝑨𝑾 𝑵𝑮 𝑨𝑷𝑳𝑰𝑲𝑨𝑺𝒀𝑶𝑵

Love life gusto? Sali sa TamVol ayaw?

Ito na ang iyong huling pagkakataon na maging bahagi ng Tamaraw Volunteers-Manila! Tara’t mag-apply at isumite ang iyong aplikasyon sa aming MS Forms upang maranasan ang pagiging tunay na boluntir na magpapalaganap ng taos-pusong paglilingkod sa loob at labas ng ating Happy Halls.

Para sa iba pang detalye at impormasyon, bisitahin ang aming official page o magpadala ng mensahe sa official page.

𝑴𝑨𝑫𝒀𝑨 𝑵𝑨 𝑺𝑨 𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑽𝑶𝑳!

🔗 https://forms.office.com/r/4naX3m83TG
🔗 https://forms.office.com/r/4naX3m83TG
🔗 https://forms.office.com/r/4naX3m83TG

Ito na ang iyong pagkakataon upang makibahagi sa aming mga layunin at isabuhay ang tunay na diwa ng #SerbisyongNAGAahon, na sumisibol mula sa panata ng malasakit, altruismo, at pagkilos para sa kapwa.

Isinulat ni Cesar Nora
Kuha nina Kai Dela Cruz at Marithell Hernandez
Inilikha ni Noemi Reyes

#AltruismAboveAndBeyond
#ActionOnTheGround

message.text:
𝑴𝑬𝑴𝑩𝑬𝑹𝑺𝑯𝑰𝑷 𝑨𝑷𝑷𝑳𝑰𝑪𝑨𝑻𝑰𝑶𝑵 | 𝑯𝑼𝑳𝑰𝑵𝑮 𝑨𝑹𝑨𝑾 𝑵𝑮 𝑨𝑷𝑳𝑰𝑲𝑨𝑺𝒀𝑶𝑵

Love life gusto? Sali sa TamVol ayaw?

Ito na ang iyong huling pagkakataon na maging bahagi ng Tamaraw Volunteers-Manila! Tara’t mag-apply at isumite ang iyong aplikasyon sa aming MS Forms upang maranasan ang pagiging tunay na boluntir na magpapalaganap ng taos-pusong paglilingkod sa loob at labas ng ating Happy Halls.

Para sa iba pang detalye at impormasyon, bisitahin ang aming official page o magpadala ng mensahe sa official page.

𝑴𝑨𝑫𝒀𝑨 𝑵𝑨 𝑺𝑨 𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑽𝑶𝑳!

🔗 https://forms.office.com/r/4naX3m83TG
🔗 https://forms.office.com/r/4naX3m83TG
🔗 https://forms.office.com/r/4naX3m83TG

Ito na ang iyong pagkakataon upang makibahagi sa aming mga layunin at isabuhay ang tunay na diwa ng #SerbisyongNAGAahon, na sumisibol mula sa panata ng malasakit, altruismo, at pagkilos para sa kapwa.

Isinulat ni Cesar Nora
Kuha nina Kai Dela Cruz at Marithell Hernandez
Inilikha ni Noemi Reyes

#AltruismAboveAndBeyond
#ActionOnTheGround

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello
